					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Unless you can store the whole subroutine/loop in RAM (so that JSR/RTS aren't executed repeatedly), it's better to just backup Y in ZP, load it with 0, do the indirect access and restore Y, with a total overhead of 8 cycles, instead of 12.</div>

